# Specification for User Story: Declare Float Variables

# Syntax: let <id> = <float>;

Parameters:

# Category 1: The structural validity of the statement

DeclarationStructure:
Valid Let Assignment.
Missing Let Keyword. [error]
Missing Variable Name. [error]
Missing Equals Sign. [error]

# Category 2: The format of the value being assigned

FloatFormat:
Positive Decimal.
Negative Decimal.
Zero Value.
Integer Value.
Trailing Dot. [error]
Non Numeric. [error]

# Category 3: How the statement ends

Terminator:
Semicolon Present.
Semicolon Missing.
